> I think it was the metal pipe that goes through the bulkhead/firewall.
There was no grommet. I replaced it with an aluminium 1/4 inch pipe from OSH
and it seems fine. Clara suggested that I take a piece of flexible hose, cut
a slot lengthwise and use that to stop the metal wearing at the bulkhead.
>
I have been able to find a suitable rubber grommet in the extensive drawers
of rubber bushings at my local ACE hardware store.

